data.description: This beautiful home is located in a gated community, providing an added sense of security and privacy. Built in 2008, this well-maintained property offers a total of 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, providing ample space for you.  This standout home has a new AC system installed in 2023, barn doors added in 2020, and the master bathroom shower has been tastefully remodeled and now has a state-of-the-art water feature in the shower, creating a luxurious and relaxing atmosphere.  Spanning across 2,143 square feet, this home offers plenty of room for all your needs. The loft area provides a versatile space that can be used as a home office, play area, or even an additional living space. As part of the gated community, you'll have access to a fantastic array of amenities. The HOA (2) fees of $238 covers the clubhouse, which includes an indoor basketball court, gym, and indoor pool. In addition, there are three outdoor pools, a splash-pad, event room, park, game room, movie room, internet, walking trails and even a sauna. These amenities provide endless opportunities for relaxation, recreation, and staying active without ever having to leave the community. This home is centrally located near various stores, food places, parks, and schools.
